<item>
<title>[TGT-4] Add methods to allow properly created threads to the ThreadManager.</title>
<link>http://issues.osjava.org/jira/browse/TGT-4</link>

                    <description>Add methods to handle adding properly created threads to the ThreadManager for control.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Properly created threads must:&lt;br/&gt;
1.) implement org.osjava.threads.ExtendedRunnable&lt;br/&gt;
2.) have a parent ThreadGroup that is an ExtendedThreadGroup already controlled by the ThreadManager.</description>
